#. [part]
#. [unit_type]: id=Free Mage, race=human, gender=female
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:123
#: Girl_unDead/units/Human_Free_Mage.cfg:20
msgid "Among mages, there are those who choose the way of love of freedom, not belonging to a group. They either live quietly alone or spend their lives on the journey belonging nowhere."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:127
msgid "They earn their livelihood solely by treating peoples' illnesses and injuries. But people do not respect them as they do the white mages. Rather, they are hated and despised like the necromancers. In any case, people ignore their existence, except when they need to ask for healing."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:131
msgid "So these mages do not live in one place for long; the inhabitants usually are unaware of what they are, as they have moved on before being discovered."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:135
msgid ""
"<span font='24'>Death</span>\n"
"<span font='16'>S0</span>"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:137
msgid "Such a life was difficult, but from such freedom, some of them acquired a magic far beyond that of the ordinary mages."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:146
msgid "Explore the village"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:163
msgid "Mom, I am going out to play."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:167
msgid "Have a nice time, but avoid the eastern swamps, as I sense a danger there."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:180
msgid "Oh, you're home already? You can play outside because the sun is still bright."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:184
msgid "Okay, my Mom."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:188
msgid "I'm curious about the swamps, maybe I shall go there... I have heard there is an old mysterious shrine there."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:192
msgid "But my Mom would scold me if she catches me with it. What should I do?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:254
msgid "Oh no, venomous creatures! I should run!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:273
msgid "I've reached the shrine, but there's not much here. I have to leave before getting darkness."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Red Mage
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:306
msgid "Hey there, young lady."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:310
msgid "Hello! But I don't know you, hmm?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Red Mage
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:314
msgid "I've traveled here from a long way, but I seem, well, to have lost my way. Is there any old shrine nearby?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:318
msgid "It's over there."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Red Mage
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:322
msgid "That's great to hear... could you please guide me there?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:326
msgid "But my Mom says I'm not allowed to go over there..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Red Mage
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:333
msgid "Even so, you can't resist my wish."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:341
msgid "What? My body is moving on its own!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:359
msgid "What now? I felt some kind of strong magic."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:364
msgid "I've reached the shrine... What do we do? Oh, he's not here..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:368
msgid "It's getting to be night, and my Mom will scold me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:385
msgid "Mom! Help me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:389
msgid "Malica! Something bad has happened to her!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:401
msgid "Phew... Just as I had intended."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/00_Death.cfg:412
msgid "This smell belongs to a very human being... Who made me awake?"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=01_Escape
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:5
msgid "Escape"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#. [side]: id=Varas, type=Ancient Lich
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:112
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:32
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:116
msgid "Undead"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:133
msgid ""
"<span font='24'>Escape <small>(Cave of the Undead)</small></span>\n"
"<span font='16'>S1</span>"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:135
msgid "Malica did not know how long she had been asleep. She felt as if she could look within a nightmare, one that was painful enough to make her wonder whether it really occurred, although she could not remember anything about it."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:144
msgid "Reach Malica to the northern signpost"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:148
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:105
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:173
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:242
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:434
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:668
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/05_Puppeteer.cfg:94
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/06_Gulf.cfg:278
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/07_Sanctuary.cfg:245
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/07_Sanctuary.cfg:626
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/08_A_Long_Day.cfg:81
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/09_Intrusion.cfg:274
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:277
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:719
msgid "Destruction of Malica"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:179
msgid "Mom..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:183
msgid "You are awake, good."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:187
msgid "Mom, what happened? You look... sad."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:191
msgid "Just a little tired, that's all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:195
msgid "Mom, I'm sorry that I went to the swamps."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:199
msgid "Everything that happens, must happen. I cannot blame you."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:202
msgid "Village Chief"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:209
msgid "Villagers are coming. I wonder how they know already?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:213
msgid "Malica, go hide in the shadows of the forest, and then escape to the north. The villagers are afraid and will think you are a demon."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:225
msgid "I am confused... I am not a scary monster!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:229
msgid "Sorry... but I don't have time to explain everything. Just escape through the shadows and avoid the sunlight."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:233
msgid "You are little, so you can hide yourself in bush."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:252
msgid "I do not understand. I cannot escape by myself!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:261
msgid "<small>The villagers have come. Please stay hidden and be quiet.</small> Yes, I hear you, I am coming."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: type=Ranger
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:265
msgid "Hey, it seems your daughter has recovered. Where is she?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:269
msgid "I will not give you Malica."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: type=Ranger
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:273
msgid "It smells of corruption and rot here... I was not mistaken in suspecting you. Search the woods and the house thoroughly."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:277
msgid "You are wrong!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: type=Ranger
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:290
msgid "Wrong? I don't think so! Such a creature should be burned to the ground and cleansed. Search quickly!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:294
msgid "Mom! I should go to her, but she told me to escape... I am sorry, Mom..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:298
msgid "Malica, run!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:320
msgid "It hurts! The sun melts my skin."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Village Chief
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:349
msgid "The kid is running away! Seize her and send her to beyond!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Red Mage
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:393
msgid "Thanks to that girl, I was able to reveal the art of resurrection. This is a good thing, but with her half-hearted body, she will not last long."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:417
msgid "No, they are burning my house! <b>Mom!</b>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Red Mage
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:462
msgid "Well, my powers were not enough... but I will soon rise again."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Red Mage
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:466
msgid "Villagers know too much, so I must get rid of all of them by Puppeteer."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:487
msgid "What happened to me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:491
msgid "Even in woods, Malica's skin and flesh melted by sunlight!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:505
msgid "Why did I have to be killed?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mother
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:509
msgid "Malica, no!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:525
msgid "There are monsters ahead! We can't move on."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Revenant
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:546
msgid "What has happened? Strange that a farmer would come to a place like this. Hmm? There's a half-rotten kid right here."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:550
msgid "Oh no! <b>Undead!</b>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Revenant
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:554
msgid "Huh? You are undead, too, do you not know it yourself?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Revenant
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:558
msgid "There is no answer and she has fainted. She's still a freshly undead. Interesting... I think I'll take her home to our master. Umm, her ear has melted and fallen off. I'll take this earring, but I can't see the other one."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:575
msgid "Oh no!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:579
msgid "Do you dare fight us humans!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:589
msgid "Rest in peace! You must die!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:593
msgid "Please no!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:604
msgid "What did I do now?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:608
msgid "This kid... used some kind of magic!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#. [message]: speaker={SECOND_ID}
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:618
#: Girl_unDead/utils/macros.cfg:44
#: Girl_unDead/utils/macros.cfg:98
msgid "I... I'm sorry."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Village Chief
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:622
msgid "This kid is dangerous! Finish her off!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01_Escape.cfg:631
msgid "Mom, sorry... I can't go any more..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=01x_Cave_of_the_Undead
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:5
msgid "Cave of the Undead"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=Varas, type=Ancient Lich
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:34
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:118
msgid "Varas"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Revenant
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:71
msgid "Boss! I have brought something unusual."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:75
msgid "Huh? You picked up a dead cat or something, didn't you? Show me anyway."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Revenant
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:79
msgid "When did I ever pick up a dead cat, huh? This one."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:89
msgid "Where am I?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:93
msgid "Hoh, a child undead is indeed unusual."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Revenant
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:97
msgid "Yeah, I think she ran away from villagers at the bottomless swamps."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:101
msgid "Girl, who are you?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Revenant
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:105
msgid "Don't be afraid. He looks scary, but won't eat you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:109
msgid "You shut up! I am asking her."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:113
msgid "My name is Malica. I am the daughter of Nina."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:117
msgid "Well, daughter of Nina. How did you die?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:121
msgid "I was attacked by monsters in the swamps... When I woke up, I was chased by the villagers. And my mother... Oh! <b>Mom!</b>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Revenant
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:125
msgid "Damn, she started to cry. I don't like kids, that's why. Undead don't cry to begin with."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:129
msgid "... Mom, no... Mom..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:133
msgid "She can't talk now. I can see that magic made her undead. I wish to observe her for a while, so you will take care of her."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Revenant
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:137
msgid "Me? Heck no! I can't take care of a kid!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:141
msgid "Ha! Haven't you brought her here? You will take care of her. Anyway, I need a name in order to call you. Do you remember your name before you died?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Revenant
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:148
msgid "My name? Ah... I have no memory of being alive."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:152
msgid "Well then, I will call you Poet, because you talk too much."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#. [unit]: type=Revenant, id=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:156
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:125
msgid "Poet"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:162
msgid "Ah... I feel tears of joy because I have a good name."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:166
msgid "It is you who said the undead don't cry, eh? And after Malica falls asleep, I want you to explore the village."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:170
msgid "You speak of her as if she is your daughter."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:174
msgid "Ah, good idea. I am adopting her."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:178
msgid "... I cannot believe this!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:182
msgid "That's not important, remember to search the village."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:186
msgid "Yes sir, oh, I forgot. Here is a dirty earring..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:190
msgid "It's mine! Please return it to me!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:194
msgid "Oh, so you do speak."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:198
msgid "My mother gave me that. There was only one from the beginning though."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:202
msgid "Show me that earring."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:206
msgid "I didn't know you like jewels."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:210
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:496
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:785
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/05_Puppeteer.cfg:228
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/08_A_Long_Day.cfg:334
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:433
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:519
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:553
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:641
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10x_Epilogue.cfg:163
msgid "..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:214
msgid "Well, I don't... Return it to Malica."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:218
msgid "But she does not have ears anymore. We could use string... make a necklace... you still have a neck."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:222
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:669
msgid "Thank you..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:226
msgid "That's the first time in my undead life I've been thanked."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:230
msgid "I doubt you were ever thanked while alive."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/01x_Cave_of_the_Undead.cfg:234
msgid "Sure. Oops, I'm going now to explore the village..."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=02_Training
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:5
msgid "Training"
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=Garak, type=Troll Warrior
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:32
msgid "Trolls"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:70
msgid "Poet searched the village and reported a surprising fact."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:74
msgid "There were no villagers, and soldiers of Wesnoth were burning down every building."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:78
msgid "That night, he captured a soldier to find out what was going on. The soldier said every villager had become a walking corpse, so the corpses and village were being burned up."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:82
msgid "Poet asked about Malica's mother, but the soldier knew nothing about her. The place where her house should have been was a field, and not even a trace remained."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:86
msgid "The existence of the village was forgotten as it was."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:90
msgid ""
"<span font='24'>Training</span>\n"
"<span font='16'>S2</span>"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:92
msgid "When Malica heard this, she became inconsolable. But slowly, she got used to her new life among the undead. Although the undead lacked human feelings, Varas and Poet were kind in comparison to how the villagers had treated her."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:101
msgid "Leave the valley"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:109
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:177
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:246
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:438
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:672
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/05_Puppeteer.cfg:98
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/06_Gulf.cfg:282
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/07_Sanctuary.cfg:249
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/07_Sanctuary.cfg:630
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/09_Intrusion.cfg:278
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:281
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:723
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:886
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:1059
msgid "Destruction of Poet"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:138
msgid "I feel so lonely being alone with you in a place like this."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:142
msgid "Hmph, I'm sorry for being an unreliable mate... but because you haven't gotten any stronger, the boss ordered us to train you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:146
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:282
msgid "I'm sorry."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:150
msgid "No need to apologize."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:154
msgid "... I wonder if I can do this? I..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:158
msgid "Are you crying, again? Where do the tears come from in your dry skull? We have no time for crying as we must rid this valley of the monsters."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:162
msgid "I'm sorry..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:166
msgid "Stop apologizing! Let's do what we are here for and then we can go home."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:170
msgid "I'm so... Yes, I should become stronger for Dad."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:179
msgid "Trolls! No one said that dirty trolls were here... We must get to the fortress to the north or we will be overpowered."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:192
msgid "Good! There is the old fort. My Princess, summon your minions there."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:196
msgid "I... I don't know if I can?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:200
msgid "They're just the lowly ones, but they'll add to the fight."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:211
msgid "You did well, my Princess."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:224
msgid "We did it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:228
msgid "Thank you, you made it happen."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:232
msgid "But you haven't grown much stronger."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:236
msgid "I'm so..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:240
msgid "Do not say sorry!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:250
msgid "Stupid girl... you had better keep yourself locked in a dark cave rather than beating the troll I threw."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:255
msgid "Who are you? For what purpose did you disturb me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:262
msgid "Listen, if you do not want to be destroyed, you better not do unnecessary things."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:269
msgid "He has disappeared..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:273
msgid "I am concerned about what he was saying. But let's go back to the cave now."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:290
msgid "Dad, Poet, I'm sorry I was not strong."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:294
msgid "Annoying! Do not say sorry, my Princess."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:298
msgid "Sorry, sorry..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:312
msgid "I can't believe I've been defeated."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:316
msgid "I was too weak to help... I'm sorry."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:320
msgid "Do not say sorry, my Princess..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/02_Training.cfg:324
#: Girl_unDead/utils/deaths.cfg:40
msgid "Poet! Oh no!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=03_Invasion_from_Orcs
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:5
msgid "Invasion from Orcs"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:22
msgid "Malica's training continued, but her progress was slow and disappointed Varas and Poet. Still, she was the adopted daughter of Varas and so, for good or bad, the other undead never doubted her abilities to lead."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:26
msgid "Soon, Malica was ordered by Varas to explore the northern valley. She departed with Poet and her soldiers."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:30
msgid ""
"<span font='24'>Invasion from Orcs</span>\n"
"<span font='16'>S3</span>"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:32
msgid "She had a foreboding feeling about this mission. Ignoring the advice and pleadings of Poet who insisted that they finish their mission there first, she returned to the cave."
msgstr ""

#. [side]: id=Orc, type=Orcish Sovereign
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:66
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:41
msgid "Orcs"
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:169
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:238
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:430
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:664
msgid "Defeat the orcish leader"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:201
msgid "Orcs here? What is happening? Is that a portal behind the throne?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:205
msgid "Poet, what are you doing here? You were to escape north with Malica."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:209
msgid "I am sorry, but she wouldn't listen to me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:213
msgid "Dad! What is happening here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Orc
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:217
msgid "There she is! The one we've been looking for."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:221
msgid "... Me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Orc
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:225
msgid "Lady, come to us and we will leave and do no further harm."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:229
msgid "Malica, don't believe them. They are lying. Just run..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:233
msgid "We don't have a much of a chance fighting. Listen to your father, escape with us."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:237
msgid "No! I can't just leave him here. Run away if you want, but I'll save my Dad or die trying."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:241
msgid "You're going to die here with him then, damn it!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:245
msgid "Malica, run! Poet, force her to leave."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:249
msgid "I'm sorry, Dad. But I can't leave you here!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:253
msgid "This is foolishness, Malica. But I am still her minion, not yours, Sir. I must follow her orders."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:265
msgid "Human mages along side orcs? These are strange times. Worse yet, from their robes, I think they are in service to the throne!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:277
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:351
msgid "So... this is my end?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:281
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:355
msgid "Dad! I couldn't save you..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:285
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:359
msgid "Malica, don't worry. Destruction for our kind is repose. Show me your earring; I would have that as my final vision."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:289
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:363
msgid "Here."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. [message]: speaker=Varas
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:293
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:367
msgid "Veronica..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:304
msgid "Dad! You orcs, I will have my revenge!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:308
msgid "Oh, this would be birth of a new Queen, but she lacks the strength."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:325
msgid "What is your purpose here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Orc
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:329
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:390
msgid "Human has gived us gold. I don't know more..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:340
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:401
msgid "He died..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:378
msgid "Dad!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:386
msgid "You came here for me and slew my father. What is your purpose here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:407
msgid "My Princess, what shall we do? If we stay here, they will come back with greater numbers. We must escape to the western valley, and rebuild the camp."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:411
msgid "I... cannot run away."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:415
msgid "From what? There are few of us here and nothing we can do will bring your father back. I do not want to die in vain."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:419
msgid "You're barely alive. Run away, if you want. I don't care. I am going to take the fight to them. I want to know why they want me. Besides, I do not think any escape would last for long."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:423
msgid "Alas! You are as stubborn as your old father... I will follow where you lead."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:427
msgid "Thank you, Poet! I did not want to have to do this alone."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/03_Invasion_from_Orcs.cfg:431
msgid "Very well!"
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=04_Revenge
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:5
msgid "Revenge"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:17
msgid ""
"<span font='24'>Revenge <small>(In the Forest)</small></span>\n"
"<span font='16'>S4</span>"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:139
msgid "Elves"
msgstr ""

#. [side]
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:150
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/07_Sanctuary.cfg:178
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/07_Sanctuary.cfg:204
msgid "Gates"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:270
msgid "We have arrived, and from somewhere the smell of humans arises."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:274
msgid "We must go forward."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:278
msgid "You've seem to have become our leader, my Princess, but I wish you were stronger..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:286
msgid "Do not apologize! You must lead us, I will conceal your weakness."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:290
msgid "I'm so... Yes... I will!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:303
msgid "Oh... here is a poor elf."
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: id=Cyclos, type=Elvish Hero
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:317
msgid "Cyclos"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:327
msgid "You undead... are you with the orcs?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:331
msgid "Oh, a bandit!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:335
msgid "... This is the first time I have been mistaken for a bandit."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:339
msgid "Um, please forget what she said. Still, we shall kill you, then go kill these orcs."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:343
msgid "Kill me! I came here prepared for death, but, orcs are my enemies too. How about make a trade between us?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:347
msgid "A trade? You are joking... There is nothing you, a captive, have that we want."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:351
msgid "You are fighting the orcs, aren't you? Their defense at the front is strong and will be difficult to break. I know a secret passage."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:355
msgid "Hm... The orcs like secret passages. What do you want in return?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:359
msgid "The orcs have kidnapped the shamans of my village and have imprisoned them somewhere in this cave... Help me free them."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:363
msgid "It would be ridiculous to try to rescue the shamans. No, your life is at an end."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:367
msgid "My life is unimportant compared to theirs. If you hurt one of them, I will kill you all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:371
msgid "Another joke! You have balls. I shall kill you now!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:375
msgid "Do so if you can, but you will never defeat the orcs."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:379
msgid "Poet! You elf! Stop! The orcs are certainly stronger than us and a frontal attack will not succeed. I promise we will not hurt your shamans. Now lead us to the secret passage."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:383
msgid "And I still demand your life."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:387
msgid "Agreed. My life is worth their rescue."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:391
msgid "You underestimate the value of your life. And what is your name? I am Malica and this is Poet."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:395
msgid "My name is Cyclos."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:399
msgid "Cyclos, fitting name. Sorry I mistook you for a bandit. By the way, why are you looking at me so seriously?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:403
msgid "Sorry. I saw woman undead for the first time. And you're wearing a rare necklace."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:407
msgid "Ah, it's my mother's earring... But I have no longer ears. So, Poet made it to necklace."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:411
msgid "Oh, we must harry! Let's go."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:415
msgid "And thus Cyclos joined Malica's fighters."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:442
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:676
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/05_Puppeteer.cfg:102
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/06_Gulf.cfg:286
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/07_Sanctuary.cfg:253
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/07_Sanctuary.cfg:634
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/08_A_Long_Day.cfg:85
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/09_Intrusion.cfg:282
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:285
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:727
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:890
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:1063
msgid "Death of Cyclos"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:462
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:754
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:827
msgid "Here is the secret passage!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:478
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:767
msgid "I have found you! But... where is Loana?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=Shaman
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:488
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:777
msgid "Ah, my Lord... The higher shamans like Loana have been taken away by soldiers of Wesnoth."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:492
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:781
msgid "No way! No..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:510
msgid "Here! Chief of enemies!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Orc
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:519
msgid "Ha, you poor undead! Can you catch me?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:523
msgid "Damn! We must find another way."
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: id=Runt, type=Troll Whelp
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:558
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:989
msgid "Runt"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:567
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:998
msgid "There is a troll runt in a cage."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:571
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:1002
msgid "That is sad... Free him."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:581
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:1012
msgid "Oh, it's going to join us. Well, it needs a name, so let's call it... Runt."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:585
msgid "And thus Runt joined Malica's fighters. If Runt dies, you lose!"
msgstr ""

#. [unit]: id=Stella, type=Elvish Marksman, gender=female
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:603
msgid "Stella"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:637
msgid "My Lord! I'm glad you are safe and sound."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:641
msgid "Oh, Stella!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:645
msgid "Why are you acting in concert with these undead?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:649
msgid "I will tell you later... Let's first slaughter these orcs."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:653
msgid "I'm ready."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:680
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/05_Puppeteer.cfg:106
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/06_Gulf.cfg:290
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/07_Sanctuary.cfg:257
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/07_Sanctuary.cfg:638
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/09_Intrusion.cfg:286
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:289
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:731
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:894
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:1067
msgid "Death of Stella"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:702
msgid "What luck, the orcs' gold!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:724
msgid "Good fortune, gold!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:791
msgid "I think there might be a secret passage... but I can't find."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:810
msgid "Why have the orcs hidden this sword here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:815
msgid "It has a power of darkness. It is useful to those who dwell in the darkness, but it harms those who live in light. Perhaps human mages hate it and so have hidden it."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:843
msgid "Tell me why you killed my Dad, and pursued me."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:848
msgid "Tell me where you have taken Loa... the shamans."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Orc
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:853
msgid "I cannot answer because I have sworn to secrecy."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:864
msgid "So, he has died... Again I have failed to find the answer."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:868
msgid "Secrecy? Ha, my Princess, what do we do now?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:872
msgid "All I know is that the king is involved. There is no alternative; we must go to the capital."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:876
msgid "Don't you think to escape somewhere to live in peace? Good, I'll follow you anywhere."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:880
msgid "Oh, I forgot. Hey, you elvish kid."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:884
msgid "I know. My life is yours."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:888
msgid "Yeah! It has been too long since I last killed an elf."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:892
msgid "Stop! Poet, such jesting is unseemly. Cyclos, do you really not regret dying now?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:896
msgid "I made the agreement."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:900
msgid "By this agreement, we cannot kill you until we save all the elvish shamans. And you are still obligated to aid us."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:904
msgid "I will be your shield... good."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:908
msgid "Damn!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:912
msgid "Cyclos! I will follow you."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:916
msgid "Stella, you must return with these shamans so our village will endure."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:920
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:569
msgid "Ah..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:924
msgid "... Stella, come with us. It never hurts to have more allies."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:928
msgid "I will go not for you, but for my Lord!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:932
msgid "All right."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:951
msgid "Elves have joined us, a troll runt comes with us. What next?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:957
msgid "Elves have joined us... What next?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: role=Shaman
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:969
msgid "Cyclos, Stella, we are returning to our village. We hope you are successful and come back safely."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04_Revenge.cfg:1016
msgid "And thus Runt joined Malica's fighters."
msgstr ""

#. [scenario]: id=04x_In_the_Forest
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:64
msgid "In the Forest"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:114
msgid "Ah... Dad..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:118
msgid "Oh, she is thinking about Varas again."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:122
msgid "Malica. A sad leader lowers the morale of all."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:126
msgid "I'm sorry. But, I am... <b>Dad!</b>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:130
msgid "I need earplugs. Cyclos, you are right, but it only makes things worse."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:134
msgid "Sorry."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:141
msgid "Malica, I lost my father twice in battle."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:145
msgid "Twice?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:149
msgid "The first time, however, he continued to live."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:153
msgid "When I was little child, there was a fierce battle against the undead in the Dark Forest. Only a few soldiers returned. My father was not among them."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:158
msgid "<small>Maybe I was in that fight...</small>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:165
msgid "Everyone thought he had died. And because my mother was already dead, I was raised by my aunt."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:169
msgid "Did that make you sad?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:173
msgid "Of course."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:177
msgid "Did you cry?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:181
msgid "A little... because I was so young."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:185
msgid "Several years later he came back. But he never spoke of what happened."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:189
msgid "It was good to have your father return home safely."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:193
msgid "I returned to live with him and he taught me how to wield a sword."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:197
msgid "It was a battle against the undead at Thirsty Mountain. And it became a fight more fierce than we anticipated."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:204
msgid "<small>Maybe I was there.<small>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:211
msgid "I wanted to prove myself. I took an opportunity to attack, but instead of success that undead warrior cut my eye."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:215
msgid "I grieve for you!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:222
msgid "<small>Oh... I remember cutting a young elf.</small>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:229
msgid "Before that undead could kill me, my father intervened. I survived, but that cruel undead monster killed him."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:233
msgid "Oh, how terrible!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:240
msgid "<small>Surely... I have killed his father!</small>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:247
msgid "My hatred for that undead warrior exists still. If I find that undead, I will avenge my father!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:251
msgid "If you find him, then I will help!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:258
msgid "<small>This boy is really stupid! And Malica forgets that she herself is undead! I shall not reveal that I killed his father. It is fortunate that elves cannot discern between the faces of the undead.</small>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:265
msgid "Since that day, I have never shown weakness to others, neither to enemies, nor to friends."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:270
msgid "<small>I wonder if I can ever become strong like him?</small>"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:277
msgid "(<i>whispering</i>) Malica?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:281
msgid "Stella, what?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:285
msgid "The fact is that Cyclos was a terrible crybaby."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:289
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:293
msgid "Yes. We were childhood friends, so I know him well. He would immediately start crying whenever we teased him. It was funny, and he was very cute."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:297
msgid "Well, Cyclos is. And you were a bad girl."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:301
msgid "Ha ha ha..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:308
msgid "Hey, what are you two whispering and laughing about?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Malica
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:312
msgid "Sorry, Cyclos, but it is not your business... Hee hee..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Stella
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:316
msgid "Yes, Cyclos, never mind... Ha ha ha..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Cyclos
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:320
msgid "I can understand men and the creatures of the forest, but women are veiled."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:324
msgid "Malica no longer cried from that day on, at least in public."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Poet
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/04x_In_the_Forest.cfg:332
msgid "Hey, we're out of the forest."
msgstr ""

