#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/09_Intrusion.cfg:189
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/09_Intrusion.cfg:226
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/09_Intrusion.cfg:252
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:117
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:139
#: Girl_unDead/scenarios/10_Castle.cfg:152
